<div>
  <p>
    This demo uses lossless compression (MozJPEG) to reduce the image sizes. Each
    image was compressed manually and different settings were used on each one.
    For the 1920w and 1280w images I used a quality of 50 and reduced the color
    palette slightly. For the 640w image I kept the full 256 colors and used a
    quality of 80.
  </p>
